urlText: Trackwork between Lithgow and Penrith
content:
Monday 27 to Thursday 30 July
  • Nightly from 7.30pm until 11.30pm, buses replace trains from Lithgow to Penrith.
  • The last train from the Blue Mountains leaves Mount Victoria at 19:01, arriving Central at 21:23.
  • Nightly from 9.10pm until 3am, buses replace trains from Penrith to Lithgow.
  • The last train to the Blue Mountains leaves Central at 19:18, arriving Mount Victoria at 21:36.
  • Trains run to the normal timetable between Penrith and Central.
  • From Tuesday 28 until Friday 31 July, each morning, buses replace the 02:43 Mount Victoria to Central train between Mount Victoria and Penrith.
  • Plan your trip before you travel for up-to-date information.
Bus routes

7BM: Katoomba, then all stations to Lithgow and return
41BM: Penrith, then all stations to Katoomba and return
43BM: Penrith, Blaxland, Springwood, Katoomba, then all stations to Lithgow and return
46BM: Penrith, Blaxland, Springwood, Katoomba, then all stations to Mount Victoria and return
subtitle: Trackwork between Lithgow and Penrith

urlText: Trackwork between Bomaderry and Wollongong
content:
Saturday 1 and Sunday 2 August
  • Buses replace trains between Bomaderry and Wollongong.
  • Trains run between Port Kembla, Wollongong and Bondi Junction, some to a changed timetable.
  • Plan your trip before you travel for up-to-date information.
Bus routes

1SC: Kiama, then all stations to Bomaderry and return
2SC: Wollongong, then Kiama and return
3SC: Wollongong, then all stations to Dapto and return
5SC: Oak Flats, then all stations to Kiama and return (by-passing Bombo in the Oak Flats direction)
6SC: Wollongong, then all stations to Oak Flats, then Kiama and return (bypassing Shellharbour Junction, Minnamurra and Bombo)
subtitle: Trackwork between Bomaderry and Wollongong

urlText: Overnight maintenance works between Circular Quay and Town Hall
content: From Monday 27 to Thursday 30 July, nightly from 8pm until 1am, light rail services will not run between Circular Quay and Town Hall on the L2 Randwick Line and the L3 Kingsford Line due to planned maintenance works in the CBD.
subtitle: Overnight maintenance works between Circular Quay and Town Hall
